&lt;li&gt;Identify, characterize, and optimize peptide labeling during the ProSE sequencing assay, leveraging mechanistic understanding of Edman chemistry and amino acid side-chain reactivity and stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop reagents and methods to maximize the stability of peptides, DNA, and peptide-DNA chimeras throughout the ProSE sequencing assay.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Chemistry team to develop amino acid side-chain protection chemistries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate compatibility of new chemistries with existing assay components, reagents, and multi-cycle sequencing conditions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate emerging chemistries from the literature and internal pipeline; synthesize and test candidate reagents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
